{"tid":1630793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我宣布連登停止分化 11點全面停止互罵","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:56.000Z","uid":38165,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"0008df61134b5e4e89c56b0aa8ea25fc00484d80","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十一點停止互罵！！！！！</span></span><br />\n我地只要保持返理性就好大機會贏<br />\n各位唔好再互屌啦<br />\n我唔知係五毛多定點<br />\n我好唔開心<br />\n我唔想輸<br />\n<br />\n大家對裝修 獅鳥問題 <br />\n可以再傾<br />\n唔好用咁重語氣 好唔好呀大家<br />\n<br />\n由6月開始講架啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割！<br />\n五毛死全家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過大家盡量唔好搞解放軍軍營啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比借口佢地反擊我地"},{"pid":"143991fb6e80b539933565c26d2ac8a226811b96","tid":1630793,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c68278d90f0679181314937955dd06390b5bbf6","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"冷靜呀大家 中共招數黎架！"},{"pid":"0e6460f0c6702b01b9a07c0dfe1b2ab8c30f7ffc","tid":1630793,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"57f8ade1462f31b8d499fa10987e3374cc9e6aab","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:55.000Z","msg":"中共又玩返人民鬥人民果招呀！"},{"pid":"4095e8a147fc905ffcf9d0479071b036308752f9","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8ed8e4d3e55237ab06d37885448e54e33529ac8","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8caaab58b4230f1c9309d03d7539967c3b7d886","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d0b7b8ee53f1e399669e51c66a5a0760b58a429","tid":1630793,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"講左好多次口罩遮唔到幾多<br />\n要做事的話 最低消費帽+面巾<br />\n<br />\n［停一停諗一諗］花少少時間睇 你覺得政府係咪真係冇做野？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630572</a><br />\n<br />\n［花10秒睇保護自已］千祈唔好以為啲狗好蠢 其實佢哋不斷做緊嘢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617712</a><br />\n<br />\n[重開][全民上鎖]立即將你嘅SIM card上鎖！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1618689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1618689</a>"},{"pid":"db682b4789fe432ea7c933ffcc9448416465479b","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3c3e21b80b4042e1ef74cb850eeeb1ccb643021","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab8247ed9a28b8be1af746d51d049b8098cff961","tid":1630793,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:44:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c799e6a12dc908ee3c0aef9771a4e11a8c9590c","tid":1630793,"uid":267105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十